%p
  First, you keep your recipients in Lists. Each list contains
  a list of unique emails, which will receive your marketing emails.
  Then, you create Letters in Lanes. Then, you link your Lists
  with Lanes, by Campaigns. Finally, you make your Letters and Campaigns
  active and they start sending emails.

%p
  More information about configuration options you can find in
